* You’re currently at **17.096** avg with ~**2.35 s**. The scoring weights length more than time, so **every 0.1 reduction** is worth a lot. Double-first acceptance + union-KNN typically yields **~0.3–0.5** improvement at (n=500) on U-square instances.
* Don’t-look and matrix-free doubles claw back most added CPU. The **118 s** guard guarantees compliance even with `restarts_number=600`.

